3. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper involves the transmission of images, which falls under the domain of computer vision. 
4. cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) - The paper involves the use of computational methods for encryption and transmission of images.
